column2: Lose conditions every interval. Health degenerates more slowly while downed.
Contains a random gold fractal weapon.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Rampager (+Precision, +Condition Damage, and +Power) stats.
Storm the Mordrem Guard prison camp, and release the prisoners.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Apothecary (+Healing Power, +Toughness, and +Condition Damage) stats.
Bleeding you inflict is more dangerous.
Cloak and leave a clone of yourself behind when struck while below the health threshold.
Increased stealth duration from mesmer skills. Gain random boons while you are in stealth.
Fields of Ruin: Stronghold of Ebonhawke
Gain regeneration and frost aura when critically hit.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Settler (+Toughness, +Healing Power, and +Condition Damage) stats.
Used by Miyani to maintain the Mystic Forge.
Salvage ascended rings for a chance to yield this item.

Minions have increased health. Gain carapace for each minion you control.
Your minions are destroyed when this trait is reassigned.
<c=@abilitytype>Survival</c> skills gain reduced recharge, grant fury, and remove conditions.
You must have Blazing Speed Mushrooms unlocked in order to use this.
<c=@abilitytype>Glamour.</c> Create an area that warps time, granting you and your allies quickness while slowing enemies.
A new version of this map is available. Would you like to travel there now?
Fields of Ruin: Last Stand Shelter
Hit up to four foes with a single shot, inflicting confusion on each foe. In addition, the first target is stunned, the second is dazed, and the third is blinded.
This item requires Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns.
You and your pet gain might when you swap pets.
Gain retaliation when you block or are struck by a critical hit. Retaliation gives you damage reduction.
Set up defenses before the Mordrem Guard attack in: %str1%
Increases precision by up to 100 points.
You may now equip three core specializations. Visit the build tab of your Hero panel to equip a third specialization.
Double-click to combine 28 Fractal Research Pages into 1 Fractal Journal. Fractal Journals can be sold to vendors or used in fractal backpack collections.
The Mordrem are invading Brisban Wildlands.
Straits of Devastation: Shark's Teeth Archipelago
Mordrem Researcher Gnash is stationed in the fortification near Charrgate Haven on Halrunting Plains.
You become invisible when immobilized and take less damage while knocked down or stunned.
Aegis heals when it blocks an attack.
Contains recipes and components for crafting the backpack Unbound.

Enemies you interrupt are inflicted with torment.
This trait can only affect enemies with defiance bars once per interval.
Straits of Devastation: Sea of Elon
<c=@abilitytype>Command.</c> Rampage with your pet, gaining stability, fury, and swiftness. You and your pet also grant might to each other when you attack.

Collect Vexa's Golem Diagnostic Reader from her lab hidden in Fireheart Rise. Interact with the remains of Old Tom in the Uncategorized fractal to analyze them.
This item only has value as part of a collection.
Fields of Ruin: The Siege Plains
Double-click to choose a Gold Fractal weapon.
Call down a cannon barrage, knocking down enemies and dealing 20%% damage to the enemy lord.
Allied players gain double effectiveness of the keep's objective aura while within the perimeter of the keep.
Drop a syringe that provides allies with quickness.

Complete daily recommended fractals to obtain fractal research pages. Combine the pages into a completed journal and exchange it for an Ascalonian Fractal Research Paper from the Ascalonian Fractal Field Researcher located at the end of the Urban Battlegrounds fractal.
